A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 1 of Title 32 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 general provisions relative to highways, bridges, and ferries, so as to authorize the
3 construction or maintenance of roads upon military bases or installations by the Department
4 of Transportation when done so through agreement with and when paid for by the United
5 States Department of Defense or other federal entity; to provide for related matters; to repeal
6 conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Chapter 1 of Title 32 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to general
10 provisions relative to highways, bridges, and ferries, is amended by revising Code
11 Section 32-1-8, relating to construction and maintenance of private roads, as follows:
12 "32-1-8.
13 (a) Except as otherwise provided for in subsection (b) of this Code section, it It shall be
14 unlawful for any official, officer, or employee of the department, the State Road and
15 Tollway Authority, the Georgia Highway Authority, or any similar authority or of any
16 county or municipality to authorize the construction or maintenance of any private road.
